title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The result of calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction is different.
EB: The result of calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction should be the same, returning user recognizable strings.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction. 2. Perform data extraction. 3. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() after data extraction. Compare the results from step 1 and step 3.
